{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/markdown-editor/","webpackCompilationHash":"1e3e2b3aceaf2ae073fa","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Beace Blog","author":"Beace Lee"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f977d0ff-dbd2-581e-90d8-ae9fc448ae6d","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>收集了一下好用的markdown编辑器，都曾经大量使用，都爱不释手。选择恐惧症。。。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<!--more-->\n<h1>1. <a href=\"https://stackedit.io/editor#\">stackedit</a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>在线编辑器</li>\n<li>支持同步google drive，github等</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/markdown-editor/1.png\" alt=\"stackedit\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://app.classeur.io/#!/files/f4MKwIwGBljQ9kG2qP9s\">beta版</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/markdown-editor/2.png\" alt=\"stackedit-beta\"></p>\n<h1>2. <a href=\"http://dillinger.io/\">dillinger</a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>在线编辑器</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>支持同步google drive，Dropbox</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/markdown-editor/4.png\" alt=\"stackedit-beta\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/markdown-editor/5.png\" alt=\"stackedit-beta\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>更有意思的是，你可以下载它的<a href=\"https://github.com/joemccann/dillinger/releases\">源码</a>到本地，启动它运行。利于搭建静态博客。</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">cd</span> dillinger\n$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -d\n$ node app</code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/markdown-editor/6.png\" alt=\"stackedit-beta\"></p>\n<h1>3. <a href=\"https://www.zybuluo.com/mdeditor\">作业部落</a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>在线编辑器+客户端</li>\n<li>部分功能付费</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/markdown-editor/7.png\" alt=\"stackedit-beta\"></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.zybuluo.com/cmd/\">作业部落客户端</a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/markdown-editor/9.png\" alt=\"stackedit-beta\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/markdown-editor/8.png\" alt=\"stackedit-beta\"></p>\n<h1>4. <a href=\"https://pandao.github.io/editor.md/\">MEditor.md</a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>开源在线markdown编辑器</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/markdown-editor/12.png\" alt=\"stackedit-beta\"></p>\n<h1>5. <a href=\"http://markdownpad.com/\">markdownpad</a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>客户端</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>只支持Windows</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/markdown-editor/13.png\" alt=\"stackedit-beta\"></p>\n<h1>6. <a href=\"http://25.io/mou/\">MOU</a></h1>\n<p>mou是非常轻量级的markdown编辑器，为止到现在唯一让我体验不好的地方就是不支持目录的功能。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/markdown-editor/10.png\" alt=\"stackedit-beta\"></p>\n<h1>7. <a href=\"https://jbt.github.io/markdown-editor/#\">还有一些字体看起来不太友好的</a></h1>\n<p><img src=\"https://images-manager.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/static/markdown-editor/11.png\" alt=\"stackedit-beta\"></p>\n<p><strong>那么问题来了，你在用哪一款呢？</strong></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"最好用的markdown编辑器汇总","date":"November 15, 2016"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/markdown-editor/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/scala-palyframework-curd-4/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"快学Scala+Playframework之增删改查—— 数据库操作（四）"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/clean-blog-by-react-and-nodejs-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Clean Blog by Node && React"}}}}}